title: Zoom on over for a look at our great 1 bed, 1 bath! 738 Sq Ft!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Cedar Green Apartments!', '1145 116th Ave NE Blaine, MN 55434', 'Rental Size:', '1 BR - 1 BA - 738 sq ft |', 'Per Month:', '$1450 |', 'Lease Length:', 'Variable', 'show contact info', 'Sitting on the north side of Minneapolis along I-35W, Blaine makes a nice, quiet hometown setting for folks who work in the Twin Cities but prefer an apartment in the suburbs.', "One of the city's key landmarks is the National Sports Center, an enormous 650-acre complex that houses 50 full-sized soccer fields, a golf course, and the largest ice arena complex in the world.", 'Our community features:', '− 5th Floor Sky View Community Room', '− Conference Room', '− Dog Park', '− Fitness Center', '− Game Room', '− Garden Plaza', '− Playground', '− Storage lockers Available', '− FOB Controlled Building Access', '− Heated, Underground Parking', '− Outdoor Fireplace, Fire Table & Courtyard', '− Outdoor Kitchen', '− Party Room', '− Pet Wash Station', 'Our unit features:', '− Central Heating & Cooling', '− Dishwasher & Garbage Disposal', '− High Speed Internet: Cable & Century', 'OnLink Ready', '− Huge Covered Deck', '− Kitchen', '− Extra Large Walk-in Closets', '− In-home Washer & Dryer', '− Quartz Countertops', '− Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Contact us for more information!', '--', 'show contact info', '--', 'Our Pet-Policy:', 'Pets - allowed Comments: We welcome your furry friends!', 'Maximum of 2 pets allowed.', 'Maximum weight of 40-60 lbs.', 'each *Breed Restrictions and Deposit Fees apply* Dog Fee & Deposit: $250 each due at time of move-in.', 'Cat Fee & Deposit: $350 each due at time of move-in.', 'Pet Rent: 45 per month only one cat allowed.', 'Website:', '<URL>/', 'Property Management:', 'Peak Living', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '556804601AB742E5']
